Class TransportCandidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.nat.TransportCandidate
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ICECandidate, TransportCandidate.Fixed

    public abstract class TransportCandidate
extends Object
    Transport candidate.

    A candidate represents the possible transport for data interchange between the two endpoints.
